          The Impacts on Various Enterprise Companies in the Healthcare Industry Due to Litigation & Investigations.
        </p>
        <img 
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dil14r8je/image/upload/v1768399475/auto-site-builder/Exceedant/image_7.jpg" 
          alt="Healthcare analysis"
          class="mt-6 w-full h-32 object-cover rounded group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
